Guide.title: How to play
Guide.Content:
The Baby In Yellow is a prominent name in the current mobile game chart. In the game, you will play the role of a baby sister and take care of a child for a few days when the child’s parents are away.

It doesn’t matter when this child is not a normal child. Here’s a kid who will turn your babysitting simulation game into a horror game. It has the power of the devil and you will have heart-stopping moments in that spooky house.

The gameplay is very simple, you just do the task of a babysitter who needs to follow the milestones that the game requires. However, there will be times when you see strange phenomena happening in this house and it can make your heart skip a beat. This is a game not for the faint of heart. If you are new to the game and do not know what to do, you can follow the instructions below.

Guide.title: Who is the baby in yellow?
Guide.Content: The game begins with you inside the home. Other than you and the baby, there is no one else in there. It’s a plain yet modern house—there are no photos, notes, or items that will give you clues as to who the baby’s parents are. All that’s left to do is tend to the baby. You will find the game’s chapter and instructions on the left side of your screen. Instructions are broken down step-by-step. For example, your first task is to feed the baby. Underneath this are bullet points on where to get the bottle and how to give the milk to the baby. The only note missing from the list of steps is that you can only carry one item at a time. This means you will need to sit the baby down in his chair before giving the milk.

Guide.title: How to install the baby in yellow?
Guide.Content:
Ready to babysit? You can install The Baby in Yellow in 4 easy steps. First, download the version that’s compatible with your operating system. Once it begins to download, you will see the ZIP file in your Downloads folder. You’ll need a ZIP file extractor like WinRAR to extract all the files to access the game’s executable file.

Other than the Linux version of the game, you will need to run both the EXE files you see in the folder. If you’ve played the game’s early access version, you’ll notice that the latest version of The Baby in Yellow looks and sounds a lot better than it did when it was first released in 2020.

You’ll immediately notice that you can see more of your environment. This is because it has better lighting. The next major change is the addition of the ambient sound effects and music. Of course, the developer—Team Terrible—has improved the ragdoll physics, addressed game flow issues, and reworked the final sequences. Altogether, the updates are sure to bring terrifyingly good fun.

Guide.title: short yet horrifying game
Guide.Content: The Baby in Yellow is a suitable babysitter simulation game for users of all skill levels. It’s a straightforward game that’s easy to play, as you will only need to click and drag certain items. In addition, you can play around with flexible game mechanics. Brave players can get a thrill out of provoking the strange little baby.

Guide.title: Babysitting takes a turn for the worst
Guide.Content: Could you make it as a babysitter? What if the baby isn’t actually a baby? The Baby in Yellow is a free horror game, wherein you play as the babysitter. Everything appears normal; you’ve fed the baby and changed his nappy. You watch television to pass the time—only to discover that the baby has made it to his parents’ bedroom. He cries incessantly, but nothing seems to soothe him, so it looks like youre in for a long night.
